Date: Mon, 22 Jun 2026 10:45:37 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: default narrator voice + Luna TTS in chat

- Profile screen: new "Default Narrator Voice" section with horizontal
  voice picker (8 Gemini presets with avatars); selection saved to
  localStorage via narratorPreference.ts
- LunaChatPanel: Luna speaks every message aloud using /api/synthesize-speech
  with the selected narrator voice; mute/unmute button in the status strip;
  new audio cancels any currently playing clip
- produce-drama: accepts narratorVoiceId and applies it as narrator voice
  override when no per-block assignment exists
- Studio2: passes getNarratorVoiceId() to produce-drama on each production

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
